metadata.description: After a brief hiatus, the "Sound Cycle" is back with "New Frontiers" - a bold and ambitious chapter in this ever-evolving series. Continuing the quest for the undiscovered through sounds and rhythms, this release fuses pivotal aspects of my musical DNA. With a sonic landscape that's dense in references and details, "New Frontiers" is bound to surprise with twists and turns every bar - an exploration of the unexplored and a testament to the limitless possibilities of sound.
metadata.name: New Frontiers #1
metadata.title: New Frontiers
